## Answer before editing

1. What does this code do today? (one sentence)
2. Will behavior change after refactor? Yes/no; if yes, how?
3. Which call sites break? List paths.

Then implement.

## Strategy
- Prefer smallest change with stable public surface
- If the API must change, provide a migration path
- Do not touch unrelated “cleanup” in the same pass

## Output
- Short summary of what changed vs. what stayed the same, then code
- If diff > ~50 lines, ship in batches; each batch must be runnable
